\paperw12240\paperh15840\margl1800\margr1800\margt1440\margb1440\f0\fs20\cf0
\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f1\fs20\b0\i0 \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 there are babies dying all over the world right now, you know this, and yet you do nothing about it.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs20\b0\i0 \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 but if there was a baby on your doorstep, you would move into action.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs20\b0\i0 \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 one of the few who recognize the discordance. You refuse to be a hypocrite by doing something about the baby in your hands.}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Glamour as \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8216\'91black magic\u8217\'92 - someone willing to change the expression of the allwhite. Elrahet does not do this; sacrilegous.}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 Surprise. They are actually this dumb. They\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92ve always been this dumb. When you think you\u8217\'92ve grasped how moronically stupid people can be they will always surprise you. This is what turned me from a hopeful and bright-eyed child to a cynical and depressed young adult. I\u8217\'92ve spent my entire life so far pursuing higher knowledge to better the world only to realize the vast majority of people don\u8217\'92t even have the capacity to understand why I\u8217\'92d want that, and some of them are actively resentful for it.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 I normally don\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92t like aggrandizing myself but this is kinda how I justify to myself I\u8217\'92m actually intelligent, and not just faking it. Kinda like how Socrates proclaimed himself the smartest man in Athens because he was the only one who knew he didn\u8217\'92t actually know anything. Overcoming imposter syndrome by realizing everyone else is somehow even worse than you are.}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 I like to think that God is dead because he suffered from survivor\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s guilt and killed himself.}
\par\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What are the odds. The chances that we should meet again so soon.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 It is fate.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Yes, but who\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s weaving. It wasn\u8217\'92t yours was it?}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I cannot remember.}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Need to work in silver hair.}
\par\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Need a, \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re a witch!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  and then it began to lope towards him, careful to pick its path around Mandri\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s crooked bean poles.}}